    "summary": "As a Climate Neutral Cities Advisor for NetZeroCities, I support our Mission Cities in reaching the goals under the European Commission's  Climate-neutral and Smart Cities Mission. Additionally, I support the facilitation of knowledge and research, engagement and capacity building of cities, stakeholders and citizens through the various services defined in this project.\n\nAt Resilient Cities Network, I support in the delivery of European programmes and global communications. I have a background in urban planning and architecture and have more than 5 years experience of working with cities. My expertise is in inclusive development, capacity building, stakeholder engagement, participation, and communication. I have worked on projects in Europe and India, in the areas of climate adaptation, urban resilience, water management, nature based solutions and energy transition. More specifically, I have worked on programmes such as the Water as Leverage for Resilient Cities Asia commissioned by the Netherlands Enterprise Agency; and Local Energy Action Plan for Bospolder-Tussendijken in Rotterdam commissioned by IABR & the City of Rotterdam.",
